possible positives: <lora:richvip_sd2.1:1.0>, cbzbb, cute, little, baby, beautiful, fantasy art, devian art, trending artstation, digital art, detailed, realistic, humanoide, character, tiny, film still of "____" , cinematic shot, "____" environment, beautiful landspace of _____, cinematic portrait of ______, cute character as a "_____"....

most important negatives (not mandatory but they help a lot) : pencil draw, bad photo, bad draw



The generated images are created using several models, some of which are the following:

  • https://civitai.com/models/11193/illuminati-diffusion-v11

  • https://civitai.com/models/15975/artius

  • https://civitai.com/models/3704/djz-neon-mutation-v21

  • https://civitai.com/models/2107/fkingscifiv2

  • https://civitai.com/models/5699/gold-armor-portraits-21-richstyle

You can also use their prompts.

You can see the prompts in the images.

-I want to thank @ElFenomenoTv for helping me create the LoRa model.

His YouTube channel:
https://www.youtube.com/@georgealanart

I've had issues getting Lora to work before, and it was resolved by installing this extension:
https://github.com/KohakuBlueleaf/a1111-sd-webui-locon


ENJOY !!!!

If you want to share the images, you can tag me on social media or in the comments! I'd LOVE to SEE what you can do with the model!

  • Twitter: @RichViip

  • Instagram: richviip

  • Reddit: Richviip

  • Discord: RichVip#6402

    If you have any doubts, you can talk to me on social media or in the comments!
